name: Flowers sprout from my head. From the HYBRIDUS series
description:
This is the second image in the HYBRIDUS series. Self-portrait created by an artist from the global south, in quarantine.

Minibio:
Artvist, performer, vegan, intersectional feminist. Roberta Nascimento is a Brazilian Artist born in Sao Paulo's suburbs. The body is her raw material for creation. And it's trough her body that she externalizes her anguish in form of art. Her works dance between performance, video art, hybrid photography, video performance and beyond, Roberta is always looking for new languages to explore, after all, she does not believe in borders for creation.

Essa é a segunda imagem da série HYBRIDUS. Autorretrato criado por uma artista do sul global, em quarentena.

995x1350 pixels
